@kiraelizaxo While the other person is speaking, I literally repeat in my head, “wait, wait, wait, wait” 
It works for me like 70% of the time. But I also say “ignore me, idk what I’m saying” often.

Spoke w/o thinking most of my childhood. Got me in a lot of trouble. Like, a lot a lot.

@tairimisuu I bottle SO much up, mostly everything. Recently came across dx from 2001, and it was noted + I smiled when talking abt getting in trouble?! 
I rarely cry, 1x/year, w/panic attack when it’s hard to regulate. 
Hardly ever let anything out that isn’t anger/frustration.
